quran[4]{c,v,t}:
  2,142,"Maa …ďeen Yim…ďe …óaay…ďe mbi': " hol ko woppani …ďe huccitirde ma…ď…ďe nde …ďe ngonndoo ndee , wi' …ďe : "Ko Alla woodani (jeyi) fu…ónaange e hiirnaange, himo Feewna mo o muuyaa fa'de laawol pooctingo"
  2,143,"Ko wano nii min mba…óiri on le√Īol kakindiingol fii yo on laato seedoytoo…ďe e dow yim…ďe …ďen, Nulaa…óo oo seeditoyoo e dow mon. Min mba…óiraani ndee hoccotirde nde ngonndo-…óaa he mayre si wonaa min ngannda oon jokkoowo Nulaa…óo oo e oon ruttotoo…óo batte bonnere mu'un, hay si tawii …óum laatike ko sattu-…óum, si wanaa e dow …ďeen …ďe Allah feewni. Woodanaani Alla yeebaade liimanaaku moo…óon .Pellet, Allah ko Hinnotoo…óo yim…ďe …ďee jurmotoo…óo."
  2,144,"Tigi min njiyii baylitogol yeeso maa ngoo he ndowgu (kammu) nguu . Maa min kuccitn ma hoccotirde weloore ma , hoccotin yeeso maa ngoo bannge Juulirde Hoormaande ndee . kala …óo ngon-…óon, kuccinee geece (jeese) mon …óee bannge mayre , Pellet, …ďeen rokkaa…ďe defte …ďee e…ďe nganndi [Al Qur'aanaare nden] ko nde goonga immorde ka (to) Joomi ma…ď…ďe, Alla wonaa belsintoo…óo ko …ďe ngollotoo koo ."
  2,145,"Mi woondii si a addanii …ďeen rokkaa…ďe deftere ndee kala maande, …ďe jokkataa (ndewataa) Qibla (huccorde) maa oo,a wonaa jokkoowo Qibla ma…ď…ďe oo ,yoga he ma…ď…ďe wonaanii jokkoo…ďe Qibla yoga.mi Woondii si a okkii belee…óe maa…ďe …ďaawo nde ari he maa e anndal, pellet, aan oon tuma a jeyaama e too√Īu…ďe …ďee."